So, where are we going, and why do we want to get there? 

All we can say for now is that when Hoodie God (who has allegedly seen Mēmo) orders us to do something, we listen. 

There will be benefits for everyone who boards a ship...

CREW MEMBER = INVITATION: ✉️ 

• If you received (or acquired) an Invitation, you are now a Crew Member! 
• You can now collab w/ Captains by providing needed materials to build
• Spot on ship is guaranteed
• Materials will come from Biomes 
• Biomes NOT needed to board ship

CAPTAIN = BLUEPRINT: 📜 

• If you received (or acquired) a Blueprint, you are now a Captain! 
• You must now oversee the construction of a ship
• Needed materials will vary based on rarity
• Materials will come from Biomes

📨 DELIVERY REVEAL IS LIVE! 📨 

Based on your delivery, you are now a:
1- Captain, or
2- Crew Member 
• https://t.co/0EgklWto0J
